Discovering that your ex may not have had genuine feelings for you can be incredibly hurtful and confusing. It's important to remember that people's emotions and actions can be complex, and relationships can be challenging to navigate. In situations like this, it's essential to prioritize your own emotional well-being. Take some time to process your feelings and allow yourself to grieve the end of the relationship. It's normal to feel anger, sadness, and confusion in such a "Thank you for being honest with me about your feelings.
